dc_description_s: Cartographic Details: Scale [1:1,800,000]."Haywood del. ; Bowen sculp." Numbered 10. Shows boundaries, rivers, and settlements. Published by Harrison as part of an apparently untitled general atlas. Relief shown pictorially.
